Former Governor of Oyo State, Senator Abiola Ajimobi has been buried. DAILY POST reports that Ajimobi who died on Thursday was buried some minutes after 10am. The remains was buried amid tight security. Our correspondent reports that a prayer is to be offered at 12 pm at his Mosque, Abiola Ajimobi Central Mosque in Oke Ado, Ibadan. Details shortlyâ€¦